# track control
<space>         -> play/pause
<ctrl>-<left>   -> restart song/go to previous song
<ctrl>-<right>  -> go to next song
<shift>-<left>  -> go back 5 sec
<shift>-<right> -> go forward 5 sec

# volume control
<ctrl>-<up>         -> increase volume
<ctrl>-<down>       -> decrease volume
<ctrl>-<shift>-<up> -> max volume


<ctrl>-n -> new playlist
<ctrl>-l -> focus on search field

